Player now has self health regeneration rate at 7 hitpoints.

Add two more terrian in the map: water and lava. Water is rendered with symbol ~,
Lava is rendered with symbol ^. Character will cannot swin in water without eqiupment
of cloak and cannot walk on lava without boots. Play health regeneration will speed up
by 5 times in water and will drop hitpoints when walking in lava.

Enable funcationality of object LIGHT, equip LIGHT will increase player vision.
Enable key control 'D': display non-tunneling distance map
Enable key control 'T': display tunneling distance map
Enable key control 'H': display hardness map
Enable key control 's': display the default (terrain) map
